For the application of TSCs, the haze value is important because it can reduce clarity when viewing something through the TSC. The haze value represents light scattering and was calculated using the following equation:4Haze(%)=TdiffuseTtotal×100%\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
